# Implementation Plan - Complete CUDA Poisson Project

The project is missing the core CUDA kernel for the Poisson iteration. The goal is to implement this kernel and the host launcher function.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> I am assuming a standard 7-point stencil (3D central finite difference) for the diffusion/Poisson equation based on the file names and structure.
> u^{n+1} = u^n + dt * ( (u_{i+1} - 2u_i + u_{i-1})/dx^2 + ... )

